lead_paragraph: Swede Anna Nordqvist became the oldest winner on the youthful LPGA Tour this year when she successfully defended her title at the ShopRite LPGA Classic in New Jersey on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Nordqvist Repeats as ShopRite LPGA Classic Winner
